  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"246\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0eia0BQCoYkYGv5KQxe7RjbcLRbFI18WBzOgXDFQNcRkteb82pictiaYGO9T2GupXgDzYMOU3Csg7Ew/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505168615\" data-ratio=\"0.42643923240938164\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2345\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6b6b5bfd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0eia0BQCoYkYGv5KQxe7RjbcLRbFI18WBzOgXDFQNcRkteb82pictiaYGO9T2GupXgDzYMOU3Csg7Ew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：艾伦</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">这个冬天，OpenAI感到格外寒冷而难熬。今年OpenAI概念股涨了74%，而谷歌概念股涨了146%，是OpenAI的两倍。昔日「救世主」OpenAI跌落神坛，深陷2070亿美元的资金预估缺口与信任危机；而老巨头谷歌凭借深厚家底强势复仇。当AI狂热撞上冰冷账单，一场关于信仰、资本与生存的残酷博弈正在上演，神话终将被现实戳穿。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">曾几何时，奥特曼像是手握普罗米修斯之火的先知，OpenAI的每一次发布会都能引发全球的彻夜狂欢。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwn2sbk3cw\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"802\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1232\" data-imgfileid=\"505168608\" data-ratio=\"1.4259259259259258\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;background-color: transparent;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"864\" data-width=\"864\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d9d55cb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0eia0BQCoYkYGv5KQxe7RjbkUvlD5NS1WWUY50U5XiakdU80jYic2f4AgG26uYc7EMBDbLYIJxxFRrA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图片系Nano Banana Pro生成</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那时候，我们谈论的是AGI何时接管世界，是人类的终极命运。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，最近华尔街吹来的冷风，却极其残酷地将这层宏大的科幻滤镜撕开了一角。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通往AGI的道路上，不仅铺满了显卡，还堆满了难以偿还的账单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在几周前，OpenAI还是股市的点金石，任何与它沾边的公司都能鸡犬升天。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但现在，风向变了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 48px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这家曾被视为AI革命「执剑人」的公司，正逐渐从「救世主」变成投资人眼中的「沉重包袱」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">神坛下的裂痕</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一切的转折点，或许可以追溯到那场并不如人意的GPT-5演示。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于我们普通用户而言，ChatGPT依然聪明、好用，但在资本市场眼里，惊艳感的边际效应正在递减。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与此同时，作为OpenAI最大的竞争对手，谷歌旗下的Gemini模型却在一片质疑声中打赢了翻身仗。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最新的Gemini版本不仅在基准测试中彻底大幅霸榜，更重要的是，谷歌拥有OpenAI最稀缺的东西：深不见底的现金流和完整的产业链。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种对比在最近演变成了一场戏剧性的权力交接。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">奥特曼不得不宣布进入「红色警报（Code Red）」状态，而这是一个极具讽刺意味的轮回，因为两年前正是ChatGPT逼得谷歌拉响了红色警报。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">拓展阅读：</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&amp;mid=2652650644&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=bb4e226ea4243ef1abe59320173078d3&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"奥特曼怕了！GPT-5.5「大蒜」决战谷歌，红色警报紧急拉响\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">奥特曼怕了！GPT-5.5「大蒜」决战谷歌，红色警报紧急拉响</span></a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 48px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在，「攻守之势异也」，OpenAI被迫暂停了部分探索性项目，全力修补ChatGPT的质量，试图夺回正在流失的口碑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">2070亿美元的豪赌，与焦躁的CEO</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">让投资人彻夜难眠的，不仅仅是技术迭代的放缓，更是那个令人咋舌的财务黑洞。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">汇丰银行的一份分析报告抛出了一个惊人的数字：从现在到2033年，OpenAI的收入与它宏大的支出计划之间，存在着约2070亿美元的缺口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是一个什么概念？相当于蒸发掉了半个腾讯的市值。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">面对这种质疑，OpenAI管理层的反应却显得有些动作变形。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"375\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1334\" data-imgfileid=\"505168610\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eb7fa20f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0eia0BQCoYkYGv5KQxe7RjbE8kTbcTqzVNbO0ol3ianCdibXJlBk0d0EhArFmGyu6FRGcibSYLgP70Dw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">OpenAI&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">CFO&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Sarah Friar</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI CFO Sarah Friar此前曾暗示希望美国政府能为某些融资提供「担保兜底」，这番言论瞬间在华尔街炸开了锅。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">拓展阅读：</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&amp;mid=2652643827&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=f7ee30e8e4332a58590d8434704b25cc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"OpenAI试图绑架美国政府，奥特曼还有救命底牌？\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI试图绑架美国政府，奥特曼还有救命底牌？</span></a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一家宣称要引领人类未来的科技公司，怎么听起来像是一家大而不倒的银行在求救？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">尽管后来奥特曼和Friar都紧急澄清没有索要政府救助，但这颗怀疑的种子已经种下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而在播客节目《Bg2 Pod》中，当奥特曼被问及如何填补这巨大的收支鸿沟时，这位一向温文尔雅的CEO罕见地失态了：「如果你想卖掉手里的股票，我会给你找个买家——真的，够了。」</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505168609\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1305555555555555\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1298\" data-height=\"1468\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"635\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=104335d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0eia0BQCoYkYGv5KQxe7RjbVldAc0ywj1qJOGwMouWwicXU1gV44evF0xCcd7eXotzkXL0ua1V5w1Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种防御性的姿态，恰恰暴露了房间里的大象：OpenAI正在被它自己编织的「循环融资」网络所困扰。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 48px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原本的逻辑是：微软、英伟达等巨头注资OpenAI，OpenAI再用这些钱买他们的云服务和芯片。这在增长期是完美的闭环，可一旦增长放缓，这就是一场危险的债务游戏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">谷歌的复仇：不仅仅是模型之争</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在OpenAI为下一顿「算力午餐」发愁时，谷歌正在展示什么叫做「老钱（Old Money）」的底蕴。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于普通消费者来说，我们可能只看到了Gemini在Gmail和文档里的丝滑植入，但在资本看来，谷歌的护城河深得可怕。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">它不需要求任何人给它造芯片——它有自己的TPU；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">它不需要租别人的云——它就是云本身；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">它甚至不需要担心短期盈利——YouTube和搜索业务每天都在印钞票。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">反映在股市上，这是一场残酷的零和博弈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那些依附于OpenAI生态的公司，如甲骨文、AMD，股价正在遭遇抛压；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而谷歌概念股，如为谷歌数据中心提供光器件的Lumentum和制造TPU的博通，股价却在狂欢。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505168606\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8842592592592593\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1260\" data-height=\"1114\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"497\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8a86c4d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0eia0BQCoYkYGv5KQxe7RjbXmNHnOyiaOUKibufpvTdC82OfWQH7iak0bFHKc5ABia0uQrzhDj4Z1gWzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图源：彭博社</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">晨星公司的策略师Brian Colello一针见血地指出：「几个月前，人们还认定OpenAI是唯一的赢家。但现在，人们开始意识到，Alphabet似乎才拥有拼完这块AI拼图的所有碎片。」</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 48px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505168607\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5635220125786163\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"795\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"795\" data-height=\"448\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"317\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2310b2ed&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0eia0BQCoYkYGv5KQxe7RjbAp2fCW1lF90pGGJh5diaCkpLHia5ZbMjGibFGUEhl6K9wfUdNP5QODXMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">泡沫破裂，还是价值回归？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种情绪的剧变，不仅仅关乎两家公司的股价，它更像是一次对全人类AI预期的「压力测试」。</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GQG Partners的投资经理Brian Kersmanc将现在的局面比作「服用了类固醇的互联网泡沫时代」。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwn377l1e33\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505168611\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;background-color: transparent;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"600\" data-height=\"600\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=186edbf2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0eia0BQCoYkYGv5KQxe7RjbxnCMH27VldtqFDnYZZ3zGoP2MMhFSGHJ0HFrOblmnW7jtcG5BhN0CA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他担心的不是AI技术本身，而是那种盲目的狂热。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当所有的赌注都押在「模型只要变大就能产生智能」这一条路径上时，一旦物理定律和经济规律开始反击，崩塌的不仅是股价，还有公众的信心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于我们每一个期待ASI降临的普通人来说，这或许不是坏事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去两年，我们被太多的PPT、太多的「改变世界」的口号轰炸得审美疲劳。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在，OpenAI从云端跌落凡尘，开始像一家正常公司一样为盈利和产品质量焦虑，这恰恰是AI技术走出「神学阶段」，进入「工业阶段」的标志。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI的困境告诉我们，通往星辰大海的飞船，不仅需要超越光速的引擎，还需要有人为昂贵的燃料买单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而谷歌的崛起则提醒我们，在这个赢家通吃的数字世界里，拥有基础设施的人，往往比拥有梦想的人活得更久。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这场硅谷最新的权力游戏中，我们或许正在见证一个时代的注脚：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">当潮水般的信仰退去，留下的只有坚硬的算力与更加冰冷的账单；所谓神话，不过是尚未被账本戳穿的现实。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-12-07/openai-goes-from-stock-market-savior-to-anchor-as-ai-risks-mount\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-12-07/openai-goes-from-stock-market-savior-to-anchor-as-ai-risks-mount</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章指出 OpenAI 在 AI 狂热消退后陷入资金困境和信任危机，而拥有基础设施优势的谷歌则强势崛起，警示 AI 技术正从“神学阶段”迈向“工业阶段”。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章指出 OpenAI 在 AI 狂热消退后陷入资金困境和信任危机，而拥有基础设施优势的谷歌则强势崛起，警示 AI 技术正从“神学阶段”迈向“工业阶段”。",
  "summary": "文章深入分析了 OpenAI 当前面临的困境，从其曾被视为 AI“救世主”到如今面临巨大的资金缺口和信任危机。指出 GPT-5 演示的边际效应递减，以及谷歌 Gemini 模型在技术和产业链方面的强势反击，使得 OpenAI 的“红色警报”状态与其两年前逼迫谷歌的境况形成了讽刺性轮回。文章强调了 OpenAI 高达 2070 亿美元的财务缺口，以及其管理层应对质疑的焦躁态度所暴露出的“循环融资”困境。对比谷歌凭借深厚的现金流、自研 TPU 和云基础设施的优势，指出 AI 竞赛已不再单纯是模型之争，更是基础设施和资本实力的较量。最后，文章认为这种情绪剧变是对 AI 预期的“压力测试”，预示着 AI 技术将从盲目狂热回归到更注重盈利和产品质量的“工业阶段”，拥有基础设施者将更具优势。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 面临资金困境和技术创新边际效应递减双重挑战",
      "explanation": "随着市场对 AI 狂热的降温，OpenAI 的 GPT 系列产品创新度减弱，同时面临高达 2070 亿美元的资金缺口，导致其股价和市场预期遭遇抛压，使其作为“救世主”的光环逐渐褪去。"
    },
    {
      "point": "谷歌凭借深厚底蕴在 AI 竞争中强势反攻",
      "explanation": "谷歌拥有自研芯片（TPU）和自有云服务，强大的现金流和完整产业链使其在成本和基础设施上具备 OpenAI 难以比拟的优势。Gemini 模型的崛起以及在商业化应用中的深度植入，显示出谷歌长期积累的生态优势正在转化为竞争胜势。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 行业正经历从“神学阶段”向“工业阶段”的转变",
      "explanation": "文章指出，AI 技术发展正从最初的盲目狂热和对 AGI 的过度神化（“神学阶段”）回归理性。当前行业更注重实际盈利能力、产品质量、成本控制以及基础设施建设（“工业阶段”），这意味着商业模式和可持续发展将成为核心考量。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“循环融资”模式下成本与收益的错配导致 OpenAI 商业模式承压",
      "explanation": "OpenAI 与微软、英伟达等巨头的循环融资模式依赖持续增长。一旦增长放缓，对算力等基础设施的巨额投入将难以持续，暴露出 OpenAI 在寻求盈利和填补资金缺口方面的巨大压力，引发投资者担忧。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "昔日「救世主」OpenAI 跌落神坛，深陷 2070 亿美元的资金预估缺口与信任危机；而老巨头谷歌凭借深厚家底强势复仇。",
